1. Install NVIDIA drivers and tools
pacman -Sy --needed \ base-devel git curl wget \ dkms linux=headers \ nvidia-dkms nvidia-utils cuda cudnn \ python python-pip python-virtualenv
reboot machine
Check GPU with nvidia-smi, confirm GPU is listed.

2. Install Ollama (Ollama allows you to interact with LLMs locally on your machine)
curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install/sh |sh (can use bash instead)
enable the service: systemctl --user enable --now ollama

3. Pull and Run Mistral-7B
ollama pull mistral:7b (this may take some time)
ollama run mistral:7b
text should show as >>>
test with question
